# gdalbin

<!-- badges: start -->
[![OSX Build Status](http://badges.herokuapp.com/travis/mdsumner/gdalbin?branch=master&env=BUILD_NAME=osx_release&label=osx)](https://travis-ci.org/mdsumner/gdalbin)

<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of gdalbin is to see if we can install a GDAL requiring package on OSX without homebrew or apt addons.
